<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>TeamJuiceBoxIdeaz</title>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <script src="assets/jquery.min.js"></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <nav role="navigation" class="navbar navbar-default">
      <!-- Brand and toggle get grouped for better mobile display -->
      <div class="navbar-header">
        <button type="button" data-target="#navbarCollapse" data-toggle="collapse" class="navbar-toggle">
          <span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span>
          <span class="icon-bar"></span>
          <span class="icon-bar"></span>
          <span class="icon-bar"></span>
        </button>
      </div>
      <!-- Collection of nav links, forms, and other content for toggling -->
      <div id="navbarCollapse" class="collapse navbar-collapse">
        <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
          <li><%= link_to image_tag("brain3.png"), root_path %></li>
          <li><%= button_tag "Sign Up", :class => "modal-box", 'data-toggle' => 'modal', 'data-target' => "#myModal"%></li>

          <li><%= button_tag "Log In", :class => "modal-box", 'data-toggle' => 'modal', 'data-target' => "#myModal2" %></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="coffee">
      <%= image_tag "coffee.jpg", :class => "img-responsive" %>
    </div>

    <div class="main left-side clearfix">
      <div>
        <%= image_tag "lightbulb.png", :class => "left-image" %>
      </div>
      <div class="testing">
        <h2> Create and Organize Awesome Ideas!</h2>
        <p class="main-text">We think everyone has life changing thoughts everyday! We built JuiceBox Ideas so that you have a place to store these awesome ideas. Whether you want to invent the worlds first flying automobile or build the next facebook, JuiceBox is here for you. Get Started now, it's easy!</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="main clearfix test">
      <%= image_tag "friends.png", :class => "right-image" %>
      <h2 class="left-text" > Share Your Ideas with others!</h2>
      <p class="left-text main-text">We all know that working on things by yourself can get really boring. JuiceBox Ideas lets you organize and share your ideas with friends or others involved in the community. View their profile and if they're a right match then send them an invite. We are all about changing the world in a positive way!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="main left-side clearfix">
      <%= image_tag "group.png", :class => "left-image" %>
      <h2 > Join Groups and Help with Others Ideas</h2>
      <p class="main-text"> Take part in the community, join groups, meet friends and build awesome stuff. That's what JuiceBox is all about. We believe the best stuff is built in teams where each persons skills can be fully utilized. We at JuiceBox Ideas never say never!</p>
    </div>
    <%= render "users/modal" %>
    <%= render "sessions/modal" %>
  </body>
</html>
